<COREF ID="27" TYPE="IDENT">The IRA</COREF> leveled <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="27" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> accusations</COREF> at a press conference called to announce <COREF ID="27" TYPE="IDENT">the group 's</COREF> formation on September 9 .
