Drawing on the term " White Terror , " which refers to political persecution carried out by the KMT government during the 38 - year period of martial law , the three main opposition parties in the legislature have criticized the new administration for carrying out a " Green Terror " campaign -LRB- a reference to the green color of the <COREF ID="21" TYPE="IDENT">DPP</COREF> flag -RRB- .
